metadata.name: Beyond The Visible
metadata.description:
I am a photography based digital artist.

I'm re-constructing the images by using my own photos to design new places, new stories. I melt miscellaneous media, content and emotion to create an original artwork free from time. 
Can also be defined as a Photographic Matte Designer. 

This piece was the "Star" artwork from my first solo exhibition called "Are You Awake?" 
This last edition will be presented as NFT. (1/1)
100x100cm - 300dpi
As an artist I prefer to create spiritual, philosophical and abstract content to connect with the viewer.
#photography #portrait #portraitphotography #figurative #expressionist #surrealism
